              Salesforce Apex Coding

--------------------------------------------------------

        Basic Program to Print Hello World
        
--------------------------------------------------------
Coding 1: Using Static

public class Helloworld 
{
    public Static void sample()
    {
        System.debug('Hello World!');
    }

}

--------------------------------------------------------

To Execute :

Helloworld.sample();

--------------------------------------------------------

Coding 2: Calling Function using Object

public class Helloworld2 
{
    public void sample2()
    {
        System.debug('Hello World!!');
    }
}

--------------------------------------------------------

To Execute :

Helloworld2 obj = new Helloworld2();
obj.sample2();

--------------------------------------------------------
